<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Maldives Honeymoon</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="country-hero-honey" style="background: url('/img/pexels-asadphoto-1287441.jpg');">
    <h1>Maldives Honeymoon</h1>
    <p>Crystal-clear waters, private villas, and romance in every sunset</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Description -->
  <section class="country-description-honey">
    <p>
      The Maldives is a dream destination for honeymooners from Sri Lanka and beyond. With overwater bungalows, white sandy beaches, and endless ocean views, it's the perfect place to relax, reconnect, and celebrate love in paradise.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Attractions -->
  <section class="attractions-honey">
    <h2>Most Popular Honeymoon Places in the Maldives</h2>
    <div class="attraction-grid-honey">

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/0ad63615bcd955f406a6160f86abbca0.jpg" alt="Malé City">
        <h3>Malé City</h3>
        <p>The vibrant capital of the Maldives. Explore local markets, historic mosques, and colorful island life before heading to your resort.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/b9ac58b8ba8f6747c78ee4412f7f171a.jpg" alt="Hulhumalé Island">
        <h3>Hulhumalé Island</h3>
        <p>A quiet, picturesque island near the airport. Perfect for a short stay, beach walks, and sunset views on arrival or departure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/f0caebd8d5276fc90561caa6e150dead.jpg" alt="Vaadhoo Island (Sea of Stars)">
        <h3>Vaadhoo Island</h3>
        <p>Famous for the Sea of Stars phenomenon — glowing bioluminescent beaches that light up under the night sky. A magical honeymoon moment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/d5e356dfc834c87b13e3a947e77a1753.jpg" alt="Fulidhoo Island">
        <h3>Fulidhoo Island</h3>
        <p>A peaceful local island offering authentic culture, clear lagoons, and romantic beachside picnics.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/3eb3c73c6843f3a88a52ccaf58016bcc.jpg" alt="Bandos Island">
        <h3>Bandos Island</h3>
        <p>Just a short speedboat ride from Malé, this island offers diving, snorkeling, and lush resort experiences for couples.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="attraction-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/1e31c8a40ab21d3f71be0ca99465168d.jpg" alt="Baros Island">
        <h3>Baros Maldives</h3>
        <p>One of the most romantic islands in the Maldives, known for its luxury overwater villas, spa treatments, and tranquil lagoon.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hotels -->
  <section class="hotels-honey">
    <h2>Romantic Stays in the Maldives</h2>
    <div class="hotel-grid-honey">

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/514f17ca9a3d500f65229065f4869fc4.jpg" alt="Baros Maldives">
        <h3>Baros Maldives</h3>
        <p>A luxury resort with iconic overwater villas, candlelit dinners by the beach, and pristine coral reefs for snorkeling together.</p>
        <a href="https://www.baros.com/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/b38144d622c67eacaf6923c726f8d6a9.jpg" alt="Hard Rock Hotel Maldives">
        <h3>Hard Rock Hotel Maldives</h3>
        <p>Live music, beachfront fun, and stylish overwater villas make this resort perfect for fun-loving couples.</p>
        <a href="https://www.hardrockhotels.com/maldives/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/80382a1ed9fa462006de7a97021966f7.jpg" alt="Constance Halaveli">
        <h3>Constance Halaveli</h3>
        <p>Elegant overwater retreats with private plunge pools, fine dining, and a dreamy white sand setting.</p>
        <a href="https://www.constancehotels.com/en/hotels-resorts/maldives/halaveli/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/d4bced0d82662e115f7fcf6670fed2d1.jpg" alt="Taj Exotica Resort & Spa">
        <h3>Taj Exotica Resort & Spa</h3>
        <p>One of the Maldives' finest honeymoon resorts — featuring luxury villas, spa therapies, and lagoon views to remember forever.</p>
        <a href="https://www.tajhotels.com/en-in/taj/taj-exotica-maldives/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/ad8eea0abd97ecef67a5e9036d509947.jpg" alt="Velassaru Maldives">
        <h3>Velassaru Maldives</h3>
        <p>Minimalist beachfront and water villas with serene oceanfront views, perfect for peaceful honeymoon moments.</p>
        <a href="https://www.velassaru.com/" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hotel-card-honey">
        <img src="/img/1f10fdb65416e6acfba79e30e03fc928.jpg" alt="Anantara Veli Maldives Resort">
        <h3>Anantara Veli Maldives Resort</h3>
        <p>A romantic adults-only resort with luxury villas, crystal lagoons, and wellness-focused honeymoon experiences.</p>
        <a href="https://www.anantara.com/en/veli-maldives" target="_blank">View Hotel</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
